snippet.title: Brave Nu Future  Episode 40 Special    123121
snippet.description:
ROAR Media Live Presents Brave Nu Future 
 
Host Amber King 
Brave Nu Future seeks to break the chains that bind us, expose the realities behind the NWO and help the people prepare and organize to keep a free society at the end of late-stage capitalism on the brink of the automation age.
